modules.description: This module maps a read-only filesystem device into a key/value store with operations for checking key existence, retrieving values, listing directory entries, and fetching metadata like modification times and digests. It works with string-based keys and values, supporting hierarchical lookups using key prefixes. Concrete use cases include serving static files from a read-only filesystem or exposing configuration data stored in a structured directory layout.

This module maps a read-only filesystem device into a key/value store with operations to check key existence, retrieve values, list directory entries, and fetch metadata such as modification times and digests. It works with string-based keys and values, supporting hierarchical lookups via key prefixes. Concrete use cases include serving static files from a read-only filesystem or exposing structured configuration data from a directory layout.
